snippet.title: Mark Dice
snippet.description:
I'm Mark Dice and I enjoy laughing at liberal lunatics, mocking celebrity scum, and exposing the Liberal Media Industrial Complex.  You have found the BEST CONSERVATIVE CHANNEL ON YOUTUBE, so subscribe now.

On my channel we will systematically debunk fake news, push back against Big Tech's censorship of free speech online, and defend the Constitution of the United States to Make America Great Again!

This channel has over 1.5 million subscribers and more than 400 million views, and Mark's viral videos have been featured on the Fox News Channel, the Drudge Report, the Washington Times, and other media outlets around the world.  This was the first conservative YouTube channel to reach 1 million subscribers.

Mark has a bachelor's degree in Communication from California State University and is an independent media analyst and bestselling author of "Hollywood Propaganda: How TV, Movies, and Music Shape Our Culture."

Subscribe to the channel now and click the 🔔  to turn on notifications.
